```mermaid
sequenceDiagram

Browser->>Server: HTTP POST /new_note (with form data)
    Note over Server: Process form data
Note over Server: Create new note
Note over Server: Prepare redirect
Server-->>Browser: HTTP 302 Redirect to /notes

Browser->>Server: HTTP GET /notes (following redirect)
    Note over Server: Generate HTML with updated notes
Server-->>Browser: HTTP 200 OK (HTML content)

Browser->>Server: HTTP GET /main.css
    Server-->>Browser: HTTP 200 OK (CSS content)

Browser->>Server: HTTP GET /main.js
    Server-->>Browser: HTTP 200 OK (JS content)

Browser->>Server: HTTP GET /data.json
    Note over Server: Prepare JSON with all notes (including new one)
Server-->>Browser: HTTP 200 OK (JSON with updated data)

Note over Browser: Browser renders new page
```
